FreeDBConfig.mcc/FreeDBConfig.mcc

    FreeDBConfig.mcc is a subclass of Group.mui.

    It is an interface to FreeDB configuration.

    FreeDBConfig.mcc was written by Alfonso [alfie] Ranieri <alforan@tin.it>

    FreeDBConfig.mcc is under GPL .

