    All use is at your own risk, and no liability or
    responsibility is assumed. No warranties are made.

    Note that in the following the attribute scheme is [ISGN].
FreeDBConfig.mcc/MUIA_FreeDB_Config_Done

    NAME
     MUIA_FreeDB_Config_Done -- [...N], BOOL

    FUNCTION
     When the user has done (e.g. pressed "Cancel" or "Use" and so
     on) this attribute is set and notified. Useful to close the
     window the FreeDBConfig.mcc object is attached to.
FreeDBConfig.mcc/MUIM_FreeDB_Config_Break

    NAME
     MUIM_FreeDB_Config_Break

    SYNOPSIS
     DoMethod(obj,MUIM_FreeDB_Config_Break);

    FUNCTION
     If the FreeDBConfig.mcc object is downloading the sites list from
     the Internet, this method may be used to break that.

    RESULT
     None
FreeDBConfig.mcc/MUIM_FreeDB_Config_GetSites

    NAME
     MUIM_FreeDB_Config_GetSites

    SYNOPSIS
     res = DoMethod(obj,MUIM_FreeDB_Config_GetSites);

    FUNCTION
     Make the FreeDBConfig.mcc object to download the FreeDB sites
     list from the Internet.

    RESULT
     res - 0 ok, >0 error
FreeDBConfig.mcc/MUIM_FreeDB_Config_Load

    NAME
     MUIM_FreeDB_Config_Load

    SYNOPSIS
     res = DoMethod(obj,MUIM_FreeDB_Config_Load,STRPTR name);

    FUNCTION
     Load a freedb.library configuration file.

     name is the name of the file or

       MUIV_FreeDB_Config_Load_Env
       to load the ENV: default one

       MUIV_FreeDB_Config_Load_Envarc
       to load the ENVARC: default one

    RESULT
     res - 0 ok, >0 error
FreeDBConfig.mcc/MUIM_FreeDB_Config_Remove

    NAME
     MUIM_FreeDB_Config_Remove

    SYNOPSIS
     DoMethod(obj,MUIM_FreeDB_Config_Remove,Object *parent);

    FUNCTION
     If you want to remove the FreeDBConfig.mcc object, please,
     invoke this method.

     parent is the object the FreeDBConfig.mcc object is attached to
     or NULL.

     In practice, instead of doing:

      DoMethod(parent,OM_REMMEMBER,obj);

     do:

      DoMethod(obj,MUIM_FreeDB_Config_Remove,parent);

    RESULT
     None
FreeDBConfig.mcc/MUIM_FreeDB_Config_Save

    NAME
     MUIM_FreeDB_Config_Save

    SYNOPSIS
     res = DoMethod(obj,MUIM_FreeDB_Config_Save,STRPTR name);

    FUNCTION
     Save the configuration to a freedb.library configuration file.

     name is the name of the file or:

      MUIV_FreeDB_Config_Save_Mode_Apply
      save to ENV: and not set MUIA_FreeDB_Config_Done

      MUIV_FreeDB_Config_Save_Mode_Use
      save to ENV: and set MUIA_FreeDB_Config_Done

      MUIV_FreeDB_Config_Save_Mode_Save
      save to ENVARC: and set MUIA_FreeDB_Config_Done

    RESULT
     res - 0 ok >0 error
